Re PEC GuarantyI just spoke to Mary Klyasheff at Peoples Energy She is ok with all changes except State of Texas She has suggested New York as a neutral state Seeing that Enovate is a joint venture between ENA and Peoples can we accept New York law on their guaranty Give me your thoughts Thanks Ted X Susan Scott PM To Ted NRON cc Subject Re PEC Guaranty Ted I made one addition Ted Chavez AM To Susan ScottET NRON cc Subject PEC Guaranty Susan Please review the following guaranty sent to us by Peoples Energy Corp PEC PEC and ENA will each guaranty of the obligations of Enovate I think the guaranty may have a different name Ill fix it Please review and let me know if it is acceptable or make necessary changes Thanks Ted X
